source.name: City Fleet Inventory
source.description: The Fleet Management Division of the General Services Agency tracks some of the City's fleet and fuel purchases. Table 1 shows the City's fleet inventory separating the information by departments and the type of vehicles. Table 2 shows the fuel dispensed by Fleet Management in the past 3 fiscal years by gallon by fuel type.
